{
  "id": "adv_card_ktn_08_01_short",
  "title": "長瀬琴乃 1話 言いそびれちゃった (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "もう年末なんですね。お仕事を沢山いただけた\nおかげで、なんだかあっという間な気がします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s already the end of the year. Thanks to having so much work‚\nI feel like the time just flew by.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "今月はかなりハードな日程だから、体調を崩さないか\n心配してたけど……みんな元気そうで良かったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This month’s schedule is pretty tight‚ so I was worried\nyou all might get sick… I’m glad to see everyone is doing well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "確かに忙しいですけど……年明けすぐの\nお仕事が終わったらオフになってますよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It is busy‚ but… We have time off\nafter we finish our first job of the new year‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "そのタイミングで、月ストのみんなと\n日帰り旅行をすることになったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Using that timing‚ we decided to go on a day trip\nwith all the Moon Tempest members.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.000000604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "プライベートで五人一緒に出かけるのは久しぶりだから\nその旅行を楽しみにして頑張ってます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s been a while since the five of us went out together privately‚\nso I’m working hard and looking forward to the trip.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.3999997457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "日帰りで時間も限られてるから\n予定をしっかり決めることにしたんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since it’s a day trip and we have limited time‚\nwe decided to plan it out carefully‚ but",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.2999997457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "「ご飯はどこで食べよう」「お土産はどこで買おうか」\nなんて話はいくらしても足りなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "discussions like 'Where should we eat?' and 'Where should we buy souvenirs?'\nnever seem to be enough…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.6000020345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっとした空き時間が出来るたびに\nみんなで何度も話し合ってます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whenever we have a little free time‚\nwe all get together and discuss them again and again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.1999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "充実したオフになりそうだな。それにしても……\n月ストでも遠出か。最近の琴乃はアクティブだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sounds like you’ll have a fulfilling break. By the way…\nMoon Tempest is going on a trip? You’ve been pretty active lately‚ Kotono.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.8,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}